		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="408" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">岩龙蜥使用双爪抓划一次，右爪造成<span color="#ffe599">40%</span><span>伤害，左爪造成</span><span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#ff794c">赤炎：</span><span>右爪划击和左爪抓划连续进行，分别造成</span><span color="#ff9999">50%,60%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#cc99ff">雳电：</span><span>左爪抓划产生2个对向的雷球；<br/></span><span color="#79b6f8">清涟：</span><span>左爪抓划即施加水环；<br/></span><span color="#77ebf8">霜霰：</span><span>左爪抓划在周围产生3个冰簇。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1087" width="439" height="316" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">岩龙蜥进行两次不同的下落攻击，第一次跳起下落造成<span color="#ffe599">40%</span><span>伤害，第二次跳起下落造成</span><span color="#ffe599">60%</span><span>伤害，第二次比第一次范围更大，时间更短。<br/></span><span color="#ff794c">赤炎：</span><span>两次下落分别造成</span><span color="#ff9999">50%,70%</span><span>伤害，每次下落会产生地刺，再次造成相同的伤害。<br/></span><span color="#cc99ff">雳电：</span><span>第一次下落产生3个雷球，第二次下落产生4个雷球；<br/></span><span color="#79b6f8">清涟：</span><span>第一次下落即施加水环；<br/></span><span color="#77ebf8">霜霰：</span><span>每次下落在周围产生3个冰簇。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="437" height="258" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">岩龙蜥蜷缩身子向玩家冲去，造成对应元素的<span color="#ffffbf">30%</span><span>伤害，若命中玩家，则立即进行下落攻击造成</span><span color="#ffe599">85%</span><span>伤害。冲刺期间</span><span color="#bfffec">碰到护盾</span><span>则会眩晕。<br/></span><span color="#ff794c">赤炎：</span><span>下落攻击造成</span><span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，产生地刺造成</span><span color="#ff9999">70%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#cc99ff">雳电：</span><span>下落产生3个雷球；<br/></span><span color="#79b6f8">清涟：</span><span>下落即施加水环；<br/></span><span color="#77ebf8">霜霰：</span><span>下落在周围产生3个冰簇。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1087" width="439" height="287" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">岩龙蜥进行左、右、砸3段攻击，每段均产生持续4段的追踪地刺波，接触造成<span color="#ffe599">16.5%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#ff794c">赤炎：</span><span>每段产生持续4段的追踪熔岩地刺波，接触造成</span><span color="#ff9999">25%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#cc99ff">雳电：</span><span>左捶、右捶产生1个雷球，捶地产生4个雷球；<br/></span><span color="#79b6f8">清涟：</span><span>左捶即施加水环；<br/></span><span color="#77ebf8">霜霰：</span><span>3段攻击分别在其右侧、左侧、前侧产生3个冰簇。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/岩龙蜥.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="618">
